<simplesect kind="par"><title></title><para>Depending upon DSP bit, the watchdog timer stops when CPU is in HALT mode. The debug behaviour is initially set as XMC_WDT_DEBUG_MODE_STOP during initialization in <ref refid="group___w_d_t_1ga44e875ad3a51f991024fc826dd309d62" kindref="member">XMC_WDT_Init()</ref>. Invoke this API to change the debug behaviour as needed later in the program. </para>
